metadata.description:
What am I doing? Honestly, a whole lot. This year I’ve been filming blockbuster movies, commercials, dropping albums and spending time with my lil grandkids. 

But I realized it’s time to give back to yall after supporting me on Sound so much. Dishin out a track for tha people. It’s called I Can’t Breathe. Yeah, baby. Oh, and there’s only 420 of em. So.. enjoy. Because Snoop Dogg said so.

1 more thing. This release is CC0 (creative commons), use it how ya like.

Pre-sale access 4 Snoop holders as of 9/21 !!
